OL,3,CCourt told Joey Barton 'crossed the
OL,4,Cline between free speech and a crime'
OL,6,FFormer footballer and manager Joey
OL,7,FBarton has appeared at Liverpool Crown
OL,8,FCourt on 12 charges of sending grossly
OL,9,Foffensive communications, relating to
OL,10,Fsocial media posts.
OL,12,FThe court heard that he 'crossed the
OL,13,Fline between free speech and a crime'
OL,14,Fwith posts on social media about
OL,15,Fbroadcaster Jeremy Vine and female
OL,16,Ftelevision pundits Eni Aluko and Lucy
OL,17,FWard.
